				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2012/12/17/19597-le-giec-admet-a-son-tour-le-role-predominant-du-soleil?replytocom=96743#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-96743", "96743", "respond", "19597")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
